{
  "texts": [
    "We use Mistral-Instruct-v0.2 and Zephyr-β, two popular openly available models, to generate instruction tuning data.",
    "Then, we adapt pretrained Mistral-7B and Mistral-7B-P3 on the generated tasks.",
    "Here we describe the process of creating synthetic datasets with Mistral-Instruct-v0.2 and Zephyr-β.",
    "We prompt these models to generate questions or hypotheses for the target unannotated text.",
    "Table 7 shows the prompts we used to generate the tasks."
  ]
}